version 0.7.0
	- Port to GUPnP 1.2 API
	- Switch build system to meson
	- Make connector search path overridable by setting DLEYNA_CONNECTOR_PATH
	  environment variable
	- Stability improvements for the task processor (PR#1 and PR#2)

